## Development Roadmap :nut_and_bolt:

Here is the roadmap + milestones we find appropriate to complete this integration 

Pre-milestone
- Release $15,000 to begin work on the initial framework 

Milestone 1 - release $10,000 upon completion 
- "General Users" can sign-in to QSTN using their Polkadot.JS wallet and from there on-board or earn their daily allotment 
- "General Users" can purchase and mint DOT NFTs to their personal Polkadot.JS wallet from our marketplace 
- "General Users" have option to create a 'blockchain timestamp' or receipt after answering a set of questions [user must pay gas fee]

Milestone 2 - release $25,000 upon completion 
- "Business Users" can sign-in to QSTN using their Polkadot.JS wallet and from there on-board or earn their daily allotment 
- "Business Users" can load their portal with DOT tokens as a reward for survey respondents 

